<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Inviting to the Anxious Seat ∆≤IT50</title>
<time_sig>C.M. 8.6.8.6.</time_sig>
<aka>Okla chi kanima hok čt</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Okla chi kanima hok čt,
 Chim anukfila h čt
 H čchi nukhaŐĪklo fehnakm čt
 Ola h čsh mintashke.

[V2]
 Chis čs pulla fehna hocha
 H čchi chuŐĪk čsh oka
 Nuktalala hinla hona,
 H čchik mihintoshke.

[V3]
 Ik kaniohmi hoh kia,
 Chis čs pulla hoka
 H čchik iŐĪ hofahyo kashke;
 Ola h čsh mintaŐĪshke.

[V4]
 Hatak h čsh hikia moma,
 Himak a fehna ka,
 Chis čs pulla Shilombish osh
 H čchi chuŐĪk čsh oka.

[V5]
 Hoyo  člhpesa hocha,
 Chi chuŐĪk čsh atukma
 Ant asitia pulla ka,
 Ish ema pullashke.

[V6]
 Chis čs pulla sa chuŐĪk čsh aŐĪ
 Ima li pullashke;
 Mom čt h čsh achi pullashke,
 Chis čs pulla hoke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>50</hymn_number>
<author>David Folsom</author>
</song>